<subSubSection pageId="37" pageNumber="636" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="37.[1447,2659,265,1084]" pageId="37" pageNumber="636">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1449,1686,814,843]" pageId="37" pageNumber="636">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Khartoum Gerbil is probably nocturnal and terrestrial, digging burrows.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
