</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="37" pageNumber="636" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="37.[1447,2659,265,1084]" pageId="37" pageNumber="636">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1451,1800,932,961]" pageId="37" pageNumber="636">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List because of controversial taxonomic status and general lack of knowledge. The Khartoum Gerbil is apparently rare.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
